Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最讓我感到安心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘記帶什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪也上過廁所了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你太悠哉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這話的媽媽 便當呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 放在廚房裡忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽看起來好像很精明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但某些地方其實少根筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 你看起來很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為我一直很期待全家人一起去看星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:11.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:11.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渾身長滿棘刺的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.24,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我與你相逢在你的故事中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:19.33,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:19.33,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}憎惡背後滿載致命的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:22.01,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:22.01,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你是否會殺死朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果能滿足一己之願?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.24,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你是否願為他人而死?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:30.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:30.34,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}二者皆同義詞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:32.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:32.91,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生存是場遊戲  即為倖存者  沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:35.50,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:35.50,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你將如何開始?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.23,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.23,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時空是穿過大門的十字路口!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.13,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.13,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你將去往何處?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.61,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.61,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你尋求著永恆之氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.53,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.53,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你為何而活?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:50.90,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:50.90,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們不知這個世界何時誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.77,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.77,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們是時空跳躍者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.78,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在這個世界裡 你一如往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.81,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.81,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一切將遵循著既定規則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:03.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:03.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是啊,我們在愛的交織中穿梭於過去及未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.28,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.28,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爆發!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:09.33,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:09.33,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}讓我們回撥一切傷痛繼而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.95,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.95,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想和你一起看群星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:15.01,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:15.01,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}穿越奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:21.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:21.82,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這並非終結
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fad(1500,0)}初始化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝被封住了 9th也被我打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你現在死掉的話 只會給因果律徒增困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把處於假死狀態下的東西復原一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 三週目的遊戲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2nd 趕快殺掉三週目的我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要殺掉她 我就能再次參加遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個三週目的世界 和三週目的阿雪一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加三週目的生存遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和上一個阿雪告別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再和下一個阿雪相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…是尚且一無所知的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是還沒有殺死爸爸和媽媽的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很瞭解妳的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 讓我來告訴妳 妳的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…未來?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:04:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道妳的未來會變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後 媽媽的心理疾病會越來越嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也因為工作而不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他根本不想回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽會越來越喜歡向妳發洩一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的責打痛苦到讓人無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是妳讓兩人吞下催眠藥 把他們關在了籠子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始只是想逃避一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想讓他們瞭解自己的痛苦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經不用再承受痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧 很難熬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…媽媽只是生病了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也只是工作很忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是爸爸還是媽媽 我都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 他們兩人會理解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候…這個時候的我依然相信會有光明的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…究竟是從哪裡開始扭曲的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…我也有必須去見的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果律的波動正在急速增大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產生源是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我還是不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很期待今天嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得現在的我 有更應該去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘烈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋頂上有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…老公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別一個人過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島 你去確認一下周圍有沒有傷患
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 因果律受到太多影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2nd 趕快殺掉那傢伙 頂替她的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情有點蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來正以驚人的速度改寫著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張臉…好像在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御目方教 總部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿大小姐 在教主大人的車裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有人想要加害父親母親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船津？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個臭丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖除掉父親母親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉以控制教團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等愚蠢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是一個獨自一人就什麼都做不到的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御目方教是拯救弱小的教團
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也絕對不會屈服於邪惡的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6th的未來居然也改變了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:08:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 6th應該要成為邪教的教主才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而5th的雙親應該會加入那個邪教才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5th的未來…會發生改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巷中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著騷動想要趁火打劫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是濫殺無辜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不出我所料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是最近出沒的那個變態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！我是正義的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島狗屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明外面那麼吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在奇怪狗狗們居然意外的很安靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向 什麼時候跟狗狗們混得這麼熟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我畢竟是爸爸的孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在慢跑前照顧牠們已經成為我每天的必修課了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事…我倒是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次教我怎麼訓練狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒童養護設施 母親之家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長找我們有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援助？對這個設施進行援助？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是小愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這邊沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒什麼問題的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像外面到處都很亂的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到天亮了新聞就會播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？市長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還處於研究階段的未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經預知了我的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到在遊戲開始之前就已經預知了遊戲的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據1st的日記來看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來的我似乎會在遊戲中敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且勝者不僅沒有拯救未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而逆流回溯到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個神之繼承者的選拔方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來得重新考慮才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持有者的未來就像多米諾骨牌一樣漸漸改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去別說再現二周目了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連遊戲自身的存在都很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}7/28 4:10\N阿雪困在幻覺空間裡了！\N不好 得救他才行！！\N7/28 4:20\N阿雪好像困在幻覺空間裡出不來了\N怎麼辦啊！\N7/28 4:30\N阿雪困在幻覺空間裡出不來了\N得想辦法才行！\N7/28 4:40\N阿雪困在幻覺空間裡出不來了\N得想辦法救他出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和阿雪在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 所以我要殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我總覺得自己有該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指你女朋友的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小雪你回想不起名字的意中人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 我們永遠都支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你…是我們的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經相信也許總有一天 能和爸爸媽媽互相理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻沒有等到這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳炸了這裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算會改變三週目的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要救她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿雪改變了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以三個人才在一起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪果然好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起她的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以回想起來了喔 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 比起失落的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選擇了重要之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己選擇的道路前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
