Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像…我是壞人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\c&H000000&\fscy200\fscx120\an5\pos(640,689)}——
