Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 我把你們三個一起殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\c&H000000&\fscy200\fscx120\an5\pos(640,689)\alpha&H11&}——
