Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜歡的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡阿雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\c&H000000&\fscy200\fscx120\an5\pos(640,689)\alpha&H22&}——
