Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
