Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\c&H000000&\fscy200\fscx120\an5\pos(640,689)\alpha&H55&}——
